8.  Create new container and mount same volume
$ docker run --name database -v mydata:/var/lib/mysql -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=666666 -e MYSQL_DATABASE=sezayirdb  -d mysql:5   	

9.Connect mysql and  you will your data
